Value.value: This clearly is the work of followers of Set who rededicated this crypt to his name.
This unholy contraption hasn't been here originally. Somebody put it here, probably to desecrate the crypt.
This is a rough iron cage filled with dried corpses. It looks quite yucky.
To frustrate looters, the builders of crypts like this often placed fake sarcophagi in a crypt.
This must be the sarcophagus of this crypt's builder. It looks undisrupted, but strangely massive...
This must be the sarcophagus of this crypt's builder. It looks undisturbed.
